---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Oregon Motorcycle Rental | Guided Singletrack for Advanced Riders | Hood River, OR"
  description="Guided dirt bike rentals on the best singletrack in Oregon and Southern Washington. Fresh KTM and Husqvarna bikes. Built for advanced riders. $375 per rider per day. Call Doug at 509-281-0156."
>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-tread"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Important update</p>
    <h1 class="display">Come ride with Doug in the <em>Arizona desert.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub"><strong>Same guide. Same bikes. Same hospitality.</strong></p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="https://arizonadirtbikerentals.com" class="btn btn-big">Visit Arizona Dirt Bike Rentals →</a>
      <a href="tel:5092810156" class="btn btn-big btn-outline-light">Call Doug · 509-281-0156</a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-note">Oregon rides are paused. The Pacific Northwest will be back when Doug returns north.</p>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="rides" id="ride">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="rides-header">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">The Ride</div>
        <h2 class="display section-title">Built for experienced riders.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ride-feature">
      <div class="ride-feature-img">
        <span class="ride-tag">Advanced Only</span>
        <img src="/images/rider-ktm.jpg" alt="KTM rider in orange gear charging up a hillside">
      </div>
      <div class="ride-feature-body">
        <h3>Advanced Rider Days</h3>
        <p>Fresh bikes dialed in right. Tell us what you want out of the day and we'll build it around you.</p>
        <ul class="ride-specs">
          <li>KTM &amp; Husqvarna</li>
          <li>150, 250, 300 2-strokes</li>
          <li>350 &amp; 450 4-strokes</li>
          <li>Full gear included</li>
          <li>Licensed, bonded, insured</li>
          <li>Se habla español</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="tel:5092810156" class="btn btn-big">Book a Day</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="proof" id="reviews">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="proof-header">
      <div class="section-label">What Riders Say</div>
      <h2 class="display section-title" style="margin: 0 auto 20px; white-space: nowrap; max-width: none;">Over 150 five-star reviews.</h2>
      <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
      <span class="count">Google &amp; Facebook verified</span>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews">
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>One of the top 3 riding days of my life. Doug is an awesome host, whether it's to put you at ease or give you a riding tip. Well-prepared KTM and Husky with top of the line accessories. I'll remember this for the rest of my life.</p>
        <cite>Charles Lapierre</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>Doug did a great job assessing my skills and picking the right trails. He took me through fun singletrack and mixed in open trails so I could catch my breath. I'll do this again next time I'm in the Northwest.</p>
        <cite>Doug Cooper</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>Bike was fresh, gear fit right, and the trails Doug picked were exactly the kind of technical riding I was hoping for. He reads riders quick and builds the day around what you're capable of. Hard to beat.</p>
        <cite>Ryan Hollister</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>Flew in from out of state and it was worth every mile. The singletrack in Oregon is something else. Doug knows every good line and keeps a strong pace without pushing past what the group can handle.</p>
        <cite>Mark Stevens</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>I've rented bikes in a lot of places. Nobody does it better than Doug. The bikes are dialed, the trails are incredible, and he's the real deal. Already planning the next trip with a couple buddies.</p>
        <cite>Jason Albrecht</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>Came up from California for a weekend of riding and Doug delivered. Two solid days of singletrack I'd never have found on my own. Great bike, great guide, zero hassle. Will be back.</p>
        <cite>Tony Marquez</cite>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="photo-break">
  <div class="photo-break-bg"></div>
  <div class="photo-break-content">
    <h2 class="display">Built for <em>singletrack.</em></h2>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why" id="why">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-image">
        <img src="/images/rider-forest.jpg" alt="Husqvarna rider on a Pacific Northwest forest singletrack trail">
      </div>
      <div class="why-text">
        <h2 class="display section-title">15 years in the saddle. Thousands of happy riders.</h2>
        <div class="stats">
          <div>
            <div class="stat-num">15+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Years guiding</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="stat-num">150+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">5-star reviews</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="stat-num">$375</div>
            <div class="stat-label">All-inclusive day</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="meet" id="meet">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="meet-grid">
      <div class="meet-img">
        <img src="/images/doug-portrait.webp" alt="Doug McDonald, owner and guide">
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">Your Guide</div>
        <h2 class="display">Meet Doug.</h2>
        <p>Doug McDonald has been running this operation since 2010. He's the guy who sets up your bike, leads the ride, and answers the phone.</p>
        <p>He'll meet you where you are as a rider and build a day around what you want out of it. That's why people come back year after year.</p>
        <p>Doug now runs the operation full-time in Wickenburg, Arizona. He started Oregon Motorcycle Rental in 2010 and may return to guide in the Pacific Northwest in the future. For now, all rides happen in the Arizona desert.</p>
        <a href="tel:5092810156" class="btn" style="margin-top: 12px;">Call Doug</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="final-cta">
  <div class="final-cta-bg"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">Ready to Ride?</div>
    <h2 class="display">Ready to ride <em>Arizona?</em></h2>
    <p class="lede"><strong>Booking is simple. Call or text Doug, tell him what you want out of the day, and he'll get you on the calendar.</strong></p>
<a href="tel:5092810156" class="final-phone">509·281·0156</a>
    <p class="final-note">Phone &amp; text · Licensed, bonded, insured · Se habla español</p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .hero { position: relative; min-height: 92vh; display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('/images/rider-forest.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; opacity: 1; }
  .hero-bg::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(95deg, rgba(23,17,12,0.78) 0%, rgba(23,17,12,0.55) 35%, rgba(23,17,12,0.15) 65%, rgba(23,17,12,0) 100%); }
  .hero-tread { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('/images/tire-tread.png') center/cover no-repeat; mix-blend-mode: screen; opacity: 0.18; pointer-events: none; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .hero-bg::after { background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(23,17,12,0.85) 0%, rgba(23,17,12,0.55) 55%, rgba(23,17,12,0.35) 100%); } }
  .hero-content { position: relative; max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px 100px; width: 100%; }
  .eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .eyebrow::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 36px; height: 3px; background: var(--rust); }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(56px, 9.5vw, 132px); max-width: 14ch; margin-bottom: 26px; color: var(--cream); text-shadow: 0 2px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--rust); }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 26px); max-width: 48ch; margin-bottom: 40px; color: rgba(253,252,249,0.85); }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .hero-note { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(253,252,249,0.85); max-width: 48ch; font-style: italic; }

  /* PRICE STRIP */
  .price-strip { background: var(--rust); color: #fff; padding: 40px 24px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .price-strip::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('/images/tire-tread.png') center/cover no-repeat; filter: invert(1) brightness(2); mix-blend-mode: soft-light; opacity: 0.35; pointer-events: none; }
  .price-strip > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .price-strip-inner { max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto; gap: 40px; align-items: center; }
  .price-tag { font-family: 'Big Shoulders Display', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 84px; line-height: 0.82; color: #fff; padding-right: 40px; border-right: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  .price-tag span { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 0.16em; margin-top: 12px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; }
  .price-includes { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px 32px; font-size: 15px; color: #fff; font-weight: 600; }
  .price-includes li { list-style: none; position: relative; padding-left: 24px; }
  .price-includes li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #fff; font-weight: 900; }
  .price-strip .btn { background: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); white-space: nowrap; }
  .price-strip .btn:hover { background: var(--cream); border-color: var(--cream); color: var(--ink); }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .price-strip-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; } .price-tag { border-right: none; border-bottom: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); padding: 0 0 24px; font-size: 68px; } }

  /* SECTION BASE */
  section { padding: 120px 0; }
  .section-label { font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
  .section-label::before { content: ''; width: 36px; height: 3px; background: var(--rust); }
  .section-title { font-size: clamp(42px, 6.5vw, 84px); max-width: 18ch; margin-bottom: 18px; color: var(--leather); }

  /* RIDES */
  .rides { background: var(--cream); }
  .rides-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 64px; align-items: end; }
  @media (min-width: 800px) { .rides-header { grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; } }
  .rides-header p { font-size: 17px; color: var(--leather-soft); max-width: 42ch; }
  .ride-feature { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); overflow: hidden; min-height: 560px; }
  @media (min-width: 900px) { .ride-feature { grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; } }
  .ride-feature-img { position: relative; min-height: 360px; overflow: hidden; }
  .ride-feature-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .ride-tag { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; background: var(--rust); color: #fff; padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; z-index: 2; }
  .ride-feature-body { padding: 56px 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; border-top: 3px solid var(--rust); }
  @media (min-width: 900px) { .ride-feature-body { border-top: none; border-left: 3px solid var(--rust); } }
  .ride-feature-body h3 { font-family: 'Big Shoulders Display', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(40px, 4.5vw, 64px); text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 22px; color: var(--leather); }
  .ride-feature-body p { color: var(--leather-soft); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 18px; }
  .ride-specs { list-style: none; margin: 8px 0 32px; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px 20px; }
  .ride-specs li { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leather); position: relative; padding-left: 22px; }
  .ride-specs li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--rust); position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: 900; }
  .ride-feature-body .btn { align-self: flex-start; }

  /* PROOF */
  .proof { background: var(--cream-soft); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .proof-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 68px; }
  .proof-header .section-label { justify-content: center; }
  .proof-header h2 { margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .proof-header .stars { font-size: 34px; letter-spacing: 8px; color: var(--rust); }
  .proof-header .count { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: var(--leather-soft); letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
  .reviews { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  @media (min-width: 700px) { .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1000px) { .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
  .review { background: #fff; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid var(--line-soft); border-top: 4px solid var(--rust); }
  .review-stars { color: var(--rust); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .review p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--leather); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .review cite { font-style: normal; font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); }

  /* PHOTO BREAK */
  .photo-break { position: relative; min-height: 60vh; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; padding: 0; }
  .photo-break-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('/images/rider-ktm.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; opacity: 0.75; }
  .photo-break-bg::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(23,17,12,0.85) 0%, rgba(23,17,12,0.55) 50%, rgba(23,17,12,0.35) 100%); }
  .photo-break-content { position: relative; max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 24px; width: 100%; }
  .photo-break h2 { font-size: clamp(40px, 6.5vw, 88px); max-width: 16ch; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .photo-break h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--rust); }
  .photo-break p { font-size: 18px; max-width: 50ch; color: rgba(253,252,249,0.85); margin-bottom: 8px; }

  /* WHY */
  .why { background: var(--cream); }
  .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: center; }
  @media (min-width: 900px) { .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  .why-image { position: relative; aspect-ratio: 4/5; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .why-image img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .why-image::before { content: 'SINCE 2010'; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; background: var(--rust); color: #fff; padding: 12px 18px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; z-index: 2; }
  .why-text p { font-size: 17px; color: var(--leather-soft); margin-bottom: 20px; max-width: 48ch; }
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 44px; border-top: 3px solid var(--rust); }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Big Shoulders Display', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 60px; line-height: 0.9; color: var(--leather); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--leather-soft); font-weight: 700; margin-top: 8px; }

  /* MEET */
  .meet { background: var(--cream-deep); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .meet-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; }
  @media (min-width: 800px) { .meet-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr; } }
  .meet-img { aspect-ratio: 1/1; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line); position: relative; }
  .meet-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 30%; }
  .meet h2 { font-size: clamp(40px, 5.5vw, 72px); margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--leather); }
  .meet p { font-size: 17px; color: var(--leather-soft); margin-bottom: 16px; max-width: 52ch; }

  /* SISTER */
  .sister { background: var(--leather); color: var(--cream); padding: 36px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .sister-inner { max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px 28px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .sister-label { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--rust); font-weight: 800; }
  .sister-text { font-size: 16px; color: var(--cream); }
  .sister a { color: var(--cream); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--rust); text-underline-offset: 4px; font-weight: 700; }
  .sister a:hover { color: var(--rust); }

  /* FINAL CTA */
  .final-cta { position: relative; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px; overflow: hidden; }
  .final-cta-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('/images/tire-tread.png') center/cover no-repeat; opacity: 0.55; }
  .final-cta-bg::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(23,17,12,0.45) 0%, rgba(23,17,12,0.85) 80%); }
  .final-cta > * { position: relative; }
  .final-cta .section-label { justify-content: center; color: var(--rust); }
  .final-cta h2 { font-size: clamp(52px, 8.5vw, 120px); margin-bottom: 28px; color: var(--cream); }
  .final-cta h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--rust); }
  .final-cta p.lede { font-size: 22px; max-width: 46ch; margin: 0 auto 32px; color: rgba(253,252,249,0.8); }
  .final-phone { font-family: 'Big Shoulders Display', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(56px, 8vw, 108px); color: var(--rust); text-decoration: none; display: block; margin: 12px 0; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .final-phone:hover { color: var(--cream); }
  .final-note { font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(253,252,249,0.55); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
